	 for toddlers and their families.\n\nLocation Link:\n\nBallard Branch\n\nR
	oom Location: Meeting Room\n\nRegistration Required: Registration is not r
	equired.\n\nDetailed Description: Early Learning is a great way for toddle
	rs and their families to develop learning\, literacy\, and language skills
	 as well as community with other families.\, We play with toys\, share boo
	ks\, socialize\, and have engaging\, educational activities that help kids
	 and their caregivers grow together.\n\nEvent Logistics: Registration is n
	ot required but these programs are very popular and the room capacity can 
	fill up quickly.\, Families of all ages are welcome\, though this early le
	arning program is intended for youth aged 1-3\, their caregivers and famil
	ies.\, Find out more about\n\nEarly Learning & Story Time\n\nprograms.\n\n
	Contact Us: If you have questions about this event\,\n\nAsk Us\n\nor call 
	206-386-4636.\n\nADA Accommodations: We can provide accommodations for peo
